productTitle: Nirvana Color Liquid Matte Lipstick Timeless L02
des: Nirvana Color features highly pigmented, creamy matte liquid lipsticks. The rich formula applies to the lips as a liquid and dry to an opaque, matte finish and does not make your lips heavy. These colors are perfect as your go-to shades and give your persona an attractive touch.

productTitle: wet n wild MegaLast Liquid Catsuit Matte Lipstick – Give Me Mocha
des: High-pigmented matte finish with some serious staying power. This lightweight formula offers precision, performance and intense pigmentation without drying the lips. Glides on glossy and transforms into high-pigmented matte finish – Lightweight formula made with serious staying power Vivid color, ultra-matte finish, comfortable wear.

productTitle: Vaseline Lip Therapy – Cocoa Butter
des: Clinically proven to help heal dry lips. Comes in a steel tin inspired by our original look.

productTitle: Freyias Strawberry LipGlam
des: Freyias LipGlam is infused with beeswax and petroleum jelly that glides on the lips with a beautiful pink shade. It is waterproof & transfer proof with a semi-matte finish. It’s moisture-retention formula helps keep the lips fresh & soft.

productTitle: Colormax Diva Glamour Matte Lipcolour – Monaco
des: Colormax proudly brings to you your lips’ best friend, the Diva Glamour Matte Lipcolour. Encompassing a palette of handpicked shades to suit every skin tone to perfection, Diva Glamour is for those who seek a little more. With a velvety soft texture, Diva Glamour promises phenomenal turnout. This unique formula locks in moisture for a long lasting matte look that feels like heaven on your lips. To sum it up, Diva Glamour is your chance to amp up the oomph factor effortlessly.
